column2: Couldn't be any nicer. at this time- no rain- clear lake.
Data taken during training session hosted by DNR rep Rachel Sabre.  Present were Diane Stollenwerk- Jeff Jones- Kevin Kubacki- Linda Laseke- and Tim Laseke
Lake high- flooded.  Runoff sediments visible as brown water all over lake however green still the primary color at deep hole.
